cdata.name: NoirBits
cdata.desc: NoirBits (NRB) The 2 minute block time aims to improve on LTC's time but not so drastic as to cause a permanent orphan problems. There are 50 million total coins with 20 coins per block and a 2 minute block time.There is an hourly retargetting with a 30 block mining confirmation and a six block transaction confirmation.
